title: User query: Plan description from client LLM
log: Create a plan that summarizes all line items shipped before a cutoff date, defined as July 1st 1998 minus 90 days. The query must group the results by return flag and line status. For each group, calculate the total quantity, total extended price, average quantity, average extended price, and the number of rows. You don't need ordering or sortineg. The output must be in textfile.

operations.table: (SELECT l_shipdate, l_quantity, l_extendedprice, l_returnflag, l_linestatus FROM lineitem) as X

operations.udf: (r: org.apache.wayang.basic.data.Record) => { val ret = r.getField(3).toString; val lin = r.getField(4).toString; val qty = r.getField(1).asInstanceOf[Int]; val price = r.getField(2).asInstanceOf[Double]; (ret, lin, qty, price, 1) }
(a: (String, String, Int, Double, Int), b: (String, String, Int, Double, Int)) => (a._1, a._2, a._3 + b._3, a._4 + b._4, a._5 + b._5)

(t: (String, String, Int, Double, Int)) => { val ret = t._1; val lin = t._2; val qty = t._3; val price = t._4; val cnt = t._5; val avgQty = qty.toDouble / cnt; val avgPrice = price / cnt; (ret, lin, qty, price, avgQty, avgPrice, cnt) }

log.thoughts: Plan filters lineitems shipped before 1998-04-02, groups by (l_returnflag, l_linestatus), aggregates sums and counts, then derives averages. Finally writes results to a text file.

title: Class: PlanMapper Mapped plan finalized for execution

data.table: (SELECT l_shipdate, l_quantity, l_extendedprice, l_returnflag, l_linestatus FROM (SELECT l_shipdate, l_quantity, l_extendedprice, l_returnflag, l_linestatus FROM lineitem) as X) as X

data.udf: (r: org.apache.wayang.basic.data.Record) => { val ret = r.getField(3).toString; val lin = r.getField(4).toString; val qty = r.getField(1).asInstanceOf[Int]; val price = r.getField(2).asInstanceOf[Double]; (ret, lin, qty, price, 1) }
(a: (String, String, Int, Double, Int), b: (String, String, Int, Double, Int)) => (a._1, a._2, a._3 + b._3, a._4 + b._4, a._5 + b._5)

(t: (String, String, Int, Double, Int)) => { val ret = t._1; val lin = t._2; val qty = t._3; val price = t._4; val cnt = t._5; val avgQty = qty.toDouble / cnt; val avgPrice = price / cnt; (ret, lin, qty, price, avgQty, avgPrice, cnt) }

(a: (String, String, Double, Double, Int), b: (String, String, Double, Double, Int)) => (a._1, a._2, a._3 + b._3, a._4 + b._4, a._5 + b._5)

(t: (String, String, Double, Double, Int)) => { val ret = t._1; val lin = t._2; val qty = t._3; val price = t._4; val cnt = t._5; val avgQty = qty / cnt; val avgPrice = price / cnt; (ret, lin, qty, price, avgQty, avgPrice, cnt) }
